Subject: [PATCH 4/7] TFLite: cmake support git clone shallow with specified
 SHA1ID

Change-Id: If5735d0322512ffdc7f341fd72570c9017e5b9c9
Signed-off-by: Othmane AHL ZOUAOUI <othmane.ahlzouaoui@st.com>
